    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i understand the theory behind it but i'm just feeling really anxious about not being able to sleep. if i just take the diazepam and then have a very small amount of wine to help mellow out the anxiety, wouldn't that just make the diazepam more effective? it feels like it would just compliment the medication's purpose rather than being a huge danger.",
